<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
<hr>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <%= image_tag "https://ss1.bdstatic.com/70cFuXSh_Q1YnxGkpoWK1HF6hhy/it/u=3527172605,3475364554&fm=26&gp=0.jpg", width: 300, alt: "profile image",class: 'profile-img'  %>
  <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-md-8">
    <p>凭借在多个行业多年的开发经验，我意识到客户与开发人员之间的典型产品创建过程存在问题。 开发人员通常在整个开发阶段都很少与客户进行交流，导致最终产品无法达到客户和最终用户寻求的目标</p>

    <p>For this reason I decided to utilize a completely different development pattern that focuses on highly focused communication and transparent design patterns. When I take on a project not only do I work to craft the application according to the client's specifications, I give daily updates to ensure that the project is aligning properly with the client's goals. The end result is the right product, delivered on time, and on budget.</p>
  
  
  </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
